{"tid":1181884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"75m追隻契弟小醜，真係痢狗先做到","createTime":"2019-06-01T21:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T14:42:26.000Z","uid":106136,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8150cab62789f0fb13d18bfbe1167ac3845fbec4","tid":1181884,"uid":106136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T21:15:28.000Z","msg":"睇住呢種柒真係令人心頭一振<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n季初洗横手搞鳩人，搞到要公海道歉，已經柒一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n季中幾條廢鳩連横自爆，又柒一鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果迫住唔屌又屌75m高追隻荷蘭狗，柒第三獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見班痢狗早兩個禮拜 J到天昏地暗，以為咩球王君臨咁巴閉啦，屌你老母一睇，嘩，水撚到吖，我以為睇緊學界啊75m 鐵衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一隊波可以由上至下都柒到咁勻循、咁立體、咁不堪入目，仲要自以為係一線班霸，世上真係得一隊臭痢狗做得到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/538208/page/1?post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/538208/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"38f4e605507b99dcb6a3c6399392a1d7118e73f6","tid":1181884,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T21:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb6f13f115a82534a0fa7ee94f58b9d94d56f65","tid":1181884,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T21:16:18.000Z","msg":"雲xx愛助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3237df45883b1ec903b1ecb9b0eaf53f2179d9cd","tid":1181884,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T21:16:56.000Z","msg":"cls燈王"},{"pid":"0f589462fc4eb45b2b65b0192ef909f60d8b9e2a","tid":1181884,"uid":43390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T21:17:06.000Z","msg":"燈到r聯都拎埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a05f6c8782b1d000c4308ac99abd357bfda146","tid":1181884,"uid":109491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T21:17:50.000Z","msg":"雲狗歸咗西啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj